: 1;\" src=\"http://i03.c.aliimg.com/img/ibank/2013/504/834/1084438405_325921619.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"结尾2_副本\" /><br class=\"img-brk\" /><br class=\"img-brk\" /><img style=\"border-style: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; zoom: 1;\" src=\"http://i04.c.aliimg.com/img/ibank/2013/717/912/1085219717_325921619.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"细节3_副本\" /><br class=\"img-brk\" /><br class=\"img-brk\" /><img style=\"border-style: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: bottom; zoom: 1;\" src=\"http://i02.c.aliimg.com/img/ibank/2013/237/912/1085219732_325921619.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"三_副本_副本\" /><br class=\"img-brk\" /><br class=\"img-brk\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\" style=\"border-bottom-color: #e6e6e6; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; padding: 10px 0px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; width: 753px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; orphans: 2; color: #666666; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_titleleft\" style=\"line-height: 25px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bold; padding: 0px;\">花粉增白乳</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork_text\" style=\"text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; width: 753px; padding: 0px;\">配方：花粉10克，黄瓜汁10毫升。 方法：将黄瓜汁和花粉混合，调制成膏状，睡前洗脸后将其抹于面部，次日清晨洗去。每2-3日一次。 作用：养颜、除皱、增白。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\" style=\"border-bottom-color: #e6e6e6; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; padding: 10px 0px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; width: 753px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; orphans: 2; color: #666666; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_titleleft\" style=\"line-height: 25px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bold; padding: 0px;\">花粉发乳</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork_text\" style=\"text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; width: 753px; padding: 0px;\">配方：破壁花粉3克，鲜牛奶5克，2%蜂胶酊1毫升（将蜂胶与医用酒精混合而成的具有一定浓度的液体）。 方法：洗净头发，将上述原料调匀后，涂抹在头发上，用手轻轻揉搓片刻，使之在头发上均匀分布，10分钟后洗净。每2-3日一次。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\" style=\"border-bottom-color: #e6e6e6; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; padding: 10px 0px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; width: 753px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; orphans: 2; color: #666666; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_titleleft\" style=\"line-height: 25px; margin: 0px; font-weight: bold; padding: 0px;\">花粉醋膏</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork_text\" style=\"text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; width: 753px; padding: 0px;\">配方：花粉30克，白醋15毫升。 方法：将花粉浸泡在白醋中12小时，捣细，过滤成膏状，洗脸后取少许于手心中，轻轻揉搓面部，每日一次。 作用：有很好的营养皮肤和增白作用，对褐斑、粉刺等有治疗效果。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\" style=\"border-bottom-color: #e6e6e6; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; padding: 10px 0px; widows: 2; margin: 0px; width: 753px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 23px; orphans: 2; color: #666666; overflow: hidden;\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_img\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0px auto; width: 750px; padding: 0px;\"><img class=\"err-product\" style=\"border-style: none; visibility: visible; vertical-align: middle; background-image: url(http://misc.360buyimg.com/lib/skin/e/i/error-jd.gif); zoom: 1;\" src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/g10/M00/04/17/rBEQWFEoQpgIAAAAAAOvIfLcHfsAAA7KgGdwvYAA685117.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>','2599','保健品	保健食品	蜂制品','北大荒','0','','','0','0',null,'1405899173','1406838340','597','data/files/store_275/goods_106/small_201407211531468159.jpg','1','2595','2596','2599','0','0.00','80','');
INSERT INTO ecm_goods ( `goods_id`, `store_id`, `type`, `goods_name`, `description`, `cate_id`, `cate_name`, `brand`, `spec_qty`, `spec_name_1`, `spec_name_2`, `if_show`, `closed`, `close_reason`, `add_time`, `last_update`, `default_spec`, `default_image`, `recommended`, `cate_id_1`, `cate_id_2`, `cate_id_3`, `cate_id_4`, `price`, `integral`, `tags` ) VALUES  ('510','275','material','福瑞堂【四大怀药】 贡菊 享古老草本智慧 品千年怀药文化 纯积分 仅需298积分','<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;怀菊花，四大怀药之一，补饮兼备，距今三千多年历史。怀菊花早在唐天宝年间就已闻名，怀庆府所产的怀菊花以其神奇的疗效为历代医家所看重。《神农本草经》中称其为上品，曰：&ldquo;久服利血气，轻身耐劳延年&rdquo;。《本草纲目》：&ldquo;服食菊花令人发乌，好颜色。&rdquo;宋代医学家苏颂曰：&ldquo;菊花处处有之，以覃地（今焦作为覃怀地）为佳。&rdquo;唐宋以后，怀菊花被列为历代贡品。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">福瑞堂贡菊</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">也叫福瑞堂珍珠菊，是怀菊花的珍稀品种，是怀菊花精品中的精品。贡菊&ldquo;形如珍珠，色似翡翠，花香持久，味爽耐泡&rdquo;，其&ldquo;色、香、味、形&rdquo;称四绝。长饮贡菊，能够清热解毒，养肝明目，利血脉。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">福瑞堂贡菊为保证&ldquo;道地血统&rdquo;，坚持&ldquo;五选&rdquo;原则：一选&ldquo;土地&rdquo;，精选北纬</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">3448</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">至</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">3530</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、东经</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">11202</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">至</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">11338</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">之间、绿色无污染的国家黄河湿地保护区土地。二选&ldquo;原地种&rdquo;，精选温县农业科学研究所采用系统选育法培育出的原地怀珍珠菊品种。三选&ldquo;种植&rdquo;，利用自然生态平衡技术，不使用农药和化肥，只施草木灰、香油饼、农家肥等有机肥，实现真正的纯天然、绿色有机食品。四选&ldquo;采收&rdquo;，贡菊的最佳采摘期只有</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">天，且只能早上采摘，亩产仅有</span><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">10</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\">公斤左右，福瑞堂贡菊坚持最佳采摘期，保证了贡菊的地道。五选&ldquo;炮制&rdquo;，采用古老的天然&ldquo;阴干法&rdquo;，保证了贡菊的挥发油含量最高，疗效最好。通过一系列的筛选，确保了福瑞堂珍珠菊的&ldquo;道地血统&rdquo;，更是</span><span style=\"color: #274e13;\">怀菊花中的精品。而且天然、绿色、健康</span><span style=\"color: #274e13;\">，是中华民族传统的保健佳品，是滋补延年和馈赠亲友之上品。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">福瑞堂贡菊的功效</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">：疏风散热，清肝明目，解毒。用于外感风热或风温初起、头痛眩晕，目赤肿痛，眼目昏花，对高血压，冠心病，视物模糊，以及上呼吸道感染引起的气管炎、扁桃体炎等效果显著。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">现代医学研究证明</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">福瑞堂贡菊有很好的搞菌扩张冠状动脉血管作用，既可内服，有可外用。菊性寒，历经寒暑，得天地之清气，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有清热、解毒、祛风、平肝、明目等功效。菊花不但有清香之气，使人神怡，而且有明目、祛风的作用，可缓解两眼昏糊、头晕、头痛等。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适宜人群</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">:</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #274e13;\">各类人群均可饮用。特别适用于高血压、冠心病、视物模糊等人群，对上呼吸道感染引起的气管炎、扁桃体炎亦有效。</span></span><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd4.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/1923411872/T29JQPXEBXXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd2.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/1923411872/T20jURXBtXXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd3.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/1923411872/T2M9cTXxNXXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd1.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/1923411872/T2oEQPXstaXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd1.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/1923411872/T2V0kPXvpaXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd1.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/1923411872/T2go3UXthXXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd4.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/1923411872/T2JEQQXERXXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd2.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/1923411872/T2NUcTXxRXXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd2.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/1923411872/T2IZ3PXxpaXXXXXXXX_!!1923411872.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"htt