t-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #6633cc; font-size: x-large; font-family: 宋体;\">好水出健康 Watertohealth</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc; font-size: large; font-family: 宋体;\">水是生命之源，人体内唾液、胃液、肠液、胰液等绝大部分都由水组成，如果无水，食物不能消化，养料不能吸收，血液不能流动，体温无法恒定，废物不能排泄。饮用好水能让人身心舒爽健康，反之，科学家发现，70%的疾病，尤其一些疑难杂症与饮用不健康的水有关，什么样的水才是健康的好水呢？</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #999933; font-family: 宋体; font-size: x-large;\">健康好水的标准 Health water criteria</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #999933; font-size: large; font-family: 宋体;\">世界卫生组织的科学家根据对长寿地区的大量调查结果进行分析，提出优质饮用水的六条标准：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\"><span style=\"color: #999933; font-size: medium;\">1、不含有害人体