or: #990033; font-size: medium;\">3、活化溶解于水中的空气量增大，水中富含氧，有补氧功能。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\"><span style=\"color: #990033; font-size: medium;\">4、溶解力高，可加速清除体内毒素和多余废物，提高免疫力，增强生命活力。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\"><span style=\"color: #990033; font-size: medium;\">5、矿物质含量适中，PH值呈碱性，避免了矿物质过多过少和PH值偏酸对人体的危害。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\"><span style=\"color: #990033; font-size: medium;\">6、可以清除自来水中的余氧。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #3300cc; font-family: 宋体; font-size: x-large;\">使用方法 The methods used</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"color: #6600cc;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #3300cc; font-size: large; font-family: 宋体;\">1、首次使用前请用热水冲洗2-4次，激活自动活水器。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 1