ns-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\">本店仓库一角</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd2.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/1575503979/T2DTNfXyhaXXXXXXXX_!!1575503979.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"color: #006600; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>体验远古矿物盐 畅爽清新负离子</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">● 喜马拉雅矿盐</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">喜马拉雅矿盐是3亿年前海水结晶演变，经过上亿年积存而成的古生代矿物盐。主要成份为氯化钠，并富含碘、钾、钙、镁、铁等对人体有益的元素，能更有效调节人体新陈代谢。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">● 喜马拉雅矿盐三大功能</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1. 释放对人体有益的负离子；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">2. 放射与人体相同频率的远红外；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">3. 提供碘、钾、钙、镁、铁等多种对人体有益的元素。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">● 亮白粒子</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1. 赋予牙膏膏体以新颖的外观，独特的口感；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">2. 增强牙膏清除牙垢、牙斑的能力，亮白牙齿。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">● 负离子矿物盐牙膏</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">益齿健负离子矿物盐牙膏，采用珍贵、稀有的喜马拉雅矿盐为原料，凝聚历史精华，以世界顶级矿物盐牙膏姿态展示在世人面前，给人类口腔健康带来革命性的突破。集矿物盐精华与现代健齿技术于一身的益齿健负离子矿物盐牙膏，给您带来全新清爽口感与卓越的健齿护龈功效，全面持久呵护您的牙齿。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">● 主要成分</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">氯化钠（喜马拉雅矿盐）、氟化钠、亮白粒子、长效薄荷。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">● 作用原理</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">运用科技手段，将喜马拉雅矿盐与纳米科技相结合，制成矿物盐牙膏；刷牙时由于口腔内温度和摩擦作用使牙膏接收能量，发生吸水融解现象，产生负离子；负离子吸附口腔内的厌氧菌落，使其不能生存复制，从而减少牙渍的形成，维护牙龈健康；并能提供天然微量矿物元素，促进口腔内的益生菌繁殖，改善牙龈周围血液循环的特性，可达到洁齿、固齿、除口腔异味等功效。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd3.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/1575503979/T2evRjXshXXXXXXXXX_!!1575503979.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1. 负离子能有效祛除牙釉质表面的细菌，并在牙齿周围形成保护层，使牙齿免受细菌的侵蚀。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd1.alicdn.com/imgextra/i1/1575503979/T21c4iXxRaXXXXXXXX_!!1575503979.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">2. 矿物盐有效维护牙龈健康，并提供多种天然微量元素，促进口腔内的益生菌繁殖，从而维护口腔健康。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">● 温馨提示</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>正确的刷牙方法</strong>：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Step1.先浸湿牙刷，挤上适量牙膏（牙膏不浸水），用清水湿润口腔；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Step2.刷牙齿唇颊面(外侧)时，将牙刷头置于牙面上，使牙刷与牙齿呈45&deg;角，刷毛头指向牙龈，轻轻颤动后，转动牙刷头。上牙从上往下刷，下牙从下往上刷，各部位重复8-10次；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Step3.刷上前牙腭面和下前牙舌面(牙内面)时，可将牙刷头竖起来刷；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Step4.最后