005/T2ZI.iXlBXXXXXXXXX_!!758780005.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top; float: none;\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/758780005/T2oEfPXopaXXXXXXXX_!!758780005.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top; float: none;\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/758780005/T2B46IXa0bXXXXXXXX_!!758780005.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /><img style=\"vertical-align: top; float: none;\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/758780005/T2QcBFXzhaXXXXXXXX-758780005.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px;\">【产品名称】</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px;\">天狮牌虫草菌丝体胶囊</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【主要原料】冬虫夏草发酵菌丝体粉</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【功效成份及含量】0.5g*100粒； 每100克含：腺苷&ge;0.15克：甘露醇&ge;6克</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【保健功能】免疫调节、抗疲劳</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【适宜人群】免疫力低下者、易疲劳者</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【食用量及食用方法】 每日1～2次，每次1～2粒</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【保质期】18个月</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【贮存方法】常温下置于阴凉干燥处</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">【官方价格】 230元</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4;\">&nbsp;产品概述：</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #404040;\">天狮虫草菌丝体胶囊以人工发酵优质虫草菌丝体为主要成分，采取先进生产工艺，利用现代高科技物分离技术，使产品有效成分含量更高，生物活性更蛋，其中很多有效成分，如虫草多糖、腺苷 含量高于天然冬虫夏草，采用胶囊剂型，吸收更完全、迅速，便于携带，使您能随时享受大自然 奇珍和高科技带给您的健康与便捷。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">产品荣誉：</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2002年 天狮虫草菌丝体胶囊被列为向欧盟市场推荐产品。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2003年 第三届中国国际保健节组委会天{虫草菌丝体胶襄十佳保健品。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2006年 天狮虫草菌丝体胶囊为中国保健品公信力产品。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2008年 天狮虫草菌丝体胶囊荣获中国保健品公信力产品。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">2010年 天狮虫草菌丝体胶囊获得&ldquo;中国保健品100公信力产品&rdquo;荣誉。</span><img style=\"vertical-align: top; float: none;\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/758780005/T2LPlhXE8aXXXXXXXX-758780005.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" />1.天狮虫草菌丝体胶囊是天然的高`效的免疫调节剂</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">2.是天然的抗生素</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">3.适度的扩张血管，增加</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">4.有抗疲劳，抗缺氧，镇静，降血脂，提高细胞抗氧化能力等药理作用。<img style=\"vertical-align: top; float: none;\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/758780005/T2fjofXhJbXXXXXXXX-758780005.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">天狮虫草菌丝体胶囊以优质虫草菌丝体为主要成分，是天然的抗生素，既能补肺阴，又能补肾阳，为治虚症、虚痛的良药。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top; float: none;\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/758780005/T2sdVvXq8bXXXXXXXX-758780005.jpg_.webp\" alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">体质弱、免疫力低下人群</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">长期吸烟、</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">处于各种疾病及手术后恢复期的患者</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">性能不佳人群</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">肝功能不以群</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">工作繁忙常感疲劳人群</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">生活压力大、睡眠不佳人群</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; line-height: 1.4; color: #404040; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">长期接触电脑、手机及各种微博设备的人群</p>','2662','保健品	保健品牌	天师','天狮','0','','','0','0',null,'1407885052','1407889260','757','data/files/store_275/goods_48/small_201408131510485287.jpg','1','2595','2644','2662','0','0.00','255','');
