ine-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\"><strong>洗涤与晾晒：</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">1、桑蚕丝忌碱性洗涤剂，应选用中性的洗衣粉、肥皂或丝绸专用洗涤（丝毛净）；应与其它衣物分开洗涤；也不宜用含氯漂白剂或洗涤剂处理。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">2、用冷水或温水洗涤，洗涤前，最好将桑蚕丝物品在水中浸泡5至10分钟左右，不宜长时间浸泡；</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">3、轻柔洗涤，不可大把拧绞，忌硬板刷刷洗；手洗为佳。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">4、洗好后人工排水时，应把它叠起来，用毛巾包卷起来挤水，此时用力要适度，绝对不允许拧绞，以免产生并丝，从而使面料受到严重损害；</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">5、如果使用普通洗衣粉或肥皂洗涤时，在洗净后的物品放入加有2到3滴醋，水中浸泡5分钟，再用清水净1至2次，这样可以中和衣服上的碱性物质，从而保持丝织物的鲜艳色泽；</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">6、一般可带水挂在衣架上并放置阴凉处晾干为宜，忌日晒、暴晒，不宜烘干；适合阴干，以免降低坚牢度及引起褪色泛黄，色泽变劣。</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; height: 2px; color: gray; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\" />\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\"><strong>保养方法：</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">1、收藏前应把桑蚕丝物品洗净、最好叠放，用布包好，最好单独存放，不可挤压；</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">2、丝绸不宜放置樟脑丸，否则白色会泛黄；</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">3、如果熨烫丝绸，可在晾到七八成干时，用白布衬在绸面熨烫，但熨斗温度不可高于</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">130℃，否则丝绸面料会损伤或&ldquo;脆化&rdquo;，影响寿命；熨烫时切忌喷水，避免出现水渍痕，影响外观。建议用蒸汽熨烫并记得垫布，免得烫黄和水渍。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">4、蚕丝不耐盐水侵蚀，所以夏季应该勤洗勤换。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">5、桑蚕丝属多孔性动物蛋白纤维，穿着后只要不脏可以挂在通风处等汗味挥发后再穿。</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; height: 2px; color: gray; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\" />\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 19.09090805053711px; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong><strong>温馨提示：桑蚕丝系列产品，不接受退换货服务。请在购买前详细咨询，多谢合作！</strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; height: 2px; color: gray;\" />\r\n<p styl