8181800842285px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-size: 14pt;\">花容道植物香氛精油</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\'; font-size: 14pt;\">-</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-size: 14pt;\">美颜紧致精油</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\'; font-size: 14pt;\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">净含量：</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-size: 14pt;\">10ML</span><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">蕴含荷荷巴油、肉桂、罗勒、迷迭香等天然精华油。紧致面部皮肤</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-size: 14pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">滋养面部松驰、浮肿的肌肤</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-size: 14pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">令其紧实、富有弹性、焕发青春光彩。</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\'; font-size: 14pt;\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">使用方法：</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\'; font-size: 14pt;\"><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">取适量按摩肌肤吸收即可</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-size: 14pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">配合花容道按摩手法使用效果更佳</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-size: 14pt;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt;\">避免使用在眼部。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1.12em; margin-bottom: 1.12em;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height: 30.909090042114258px; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\'; font-size: 16pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: #aa00ff; color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;精油的用法指南：</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一、玫瑰精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">取一滴滴肚脐。可治疗宫寒，预防子宫肌瘤及卵巢囊肿;减缓女性更年期症状,&nbsp;治疗阴道干涩，增进情欲;淡化色斑（特别是针对颧骨上的斑点。前期颧骨的斑会发红，后期会淡化）;活血化瘀;三公分以下的子宫肌瘤可以再配合口服及姜油泡脚；内火旺的人，刚滴下时会凉，如是宫寒，则会有暖流。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对红血丝，要配合面部及眼部刮痧，玫瑰1滴+洋甘菊2滴+檀香3滴 。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">长期滴玫瑰精油可以治便秘及腹部多余的赘肉，减肥。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">祛邹、紧肤、补水、美白、淡斑、增进两性关系。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二、姜油精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">取5－8滴于木桶泡脚。可治疗失眠。配合于玫瑰滴肚脐，治疗宫寒及预防子宫肌瘤。对月经期的小腹坠胀，用姜油泡脚，血块排得很快。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">与迷迭香配合，加到洗发露中，可以促生 发，防脱发，针对风湿性头痛更佳（连续洗 一个星期的头，明显改善。）</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">扭伤及瘀青处用姜油揉按效果更佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">三、茶树精油（可单独使用）</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一滴滴于内裤，可治疗妇科及男性疾病，男女皆可。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一滴滴于手心搓揉，可预防感冒及呼吸道疾病。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">取2－3滴配合姜油于木桶泡脚治脚气效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">茶树的发烧配方：3－5滴茶树＋1滴薄荷 ＋3－5滴檀香，可于耳后做淋巴排毒，配合刮痧效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">咳嗽配方：3－5滴茶树＋2－3滴尤加利＋&nbsp;5－10ML基底油，由下往上刮颈部前任脉处。2－3天效果明显。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有伤口直接用可预防伤口化脓。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">四、檀香精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">取一滴于头顶百会穴，可提神醒脑，净化磁场及气场，一极招财进宝。不可过多，多则是安神。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可防敏及抗敏的，且一级补水抗皱，且还可改善皮肤晦暗。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">女性配合玫瑰于耳后，可增加女性魅力， 催情同时还可净化耳后淋巴;&nbsp;男性则可配合茉莉。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">五、柠檬精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">取一滴于牙膏。要先刷出泡沫，再滴精油于泡沫上刷牙。可美白牙齿， 清洁口腔， 同时可补钙及坚固牙齿。（吃口香糖多会易患咽炎）</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">关节痛疼用4－5滴柠檬涂于患处可治疗痛疼。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3. 4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">－5滴柠檬＋3－5滴姜油直接涂抹可治风湿关节疼痛，且配合姜油泡脚。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对头痛，配合香橙和罗勒，右边头疼擦左边肩的大椎及颈椎处， 另一侧相反，效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">直接点涂轻微扁平尤及油脂粒，扁平尤则要先稍挑破一点点，再用牙签点涂。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">六、薰衣草精油（可单独使用）</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">百搭油。可做精油的稀释油。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一级催眠的精油。1－2滴安神，3－4滴则提神醒脑。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">手上起小湿疹，可用薰衣草调于护手霜里 涂抹或泡手，效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对霉菌性阴道炎，可用薰衣草一滴于内 裤或用于冲洗，效果比茶树强。 特别针对在春季梅雨季节。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对烧伤及烫伤，直接涂抹，效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">低血压患者慎用。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">七、薄荷精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">薄荷＋迷迭香＋香橙＋柠檬或洋甘菊各5滴治初期的肩周炎。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">防晒：蜂蜜＋100ML纯净水＋薄荷＋薰衣草精油各5滴全身喷。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">偏头痛，牙疼，胃痛：直接用薄荷于患处揉按。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">蛀牙的牙疼：用棉签于疼处加薄荷。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">八、洋甘菊精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适合敏感、干燥、脱皮的皮肤、治疗湿疹，镇定、平复情修复敏感肌肤：洋甘菊3滴+檀香2滴+薰衣草3滴+杏仁油10ml。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">改善油缺水：洋甘菊3滴+葡萄柚。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">改善肌肤干燥：洋甘菊3滴+玫瑰2滴+天竺葵1滴+甜杏油10ml。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">治肌肉酸痛及关节肿大、强化肝脏和消化系统功能。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">筋骨扭伤加冰块冷敷，效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对黑眼圈：橙花＋洋甘菊。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">九、佛手柑精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">治疗头痛、咳嗽、感冒、痛经。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适合油性皮肤、治疗痤疮及皮肤湿疹。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">改善情绪低落。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">改善肤质：佛手柑3滴+60ml薰衣草花水。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">适合调配的精油：洋甘菊、桉树、天竺葵、茉莉、薰衣草、柠檬。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十、广霍香精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对血毒性暗疮：2－3滴广霍香＋2－3滴薄荷＋3ML基础油，点涂或棉片湿敷效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">夏天用4－5滴广霍香＋3－5滴薄荷＋1滴茶勺蜂蜜＋适量纯净水配合喷面或腋下，可除腋臭。对身体防晒有利，于面部，可消暑。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">可配合香薰祛湿。滴于棉签上放于衣柜， 可防止衣物发霉，5滴广霍香＋5滴薰衣草。如果是被子，可夹在中间，衣物则放于衣柜即可。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4. 5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滴广霍香＋5滴尤加利驱蟑螂，可用以上棉球法。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十一、茉莉精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">一级丰胸。茉莉＋薰衣草＋肉桂可修复妊娠纹。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">茉莉＋薰衣草＋玫瑰各3－5滴＋10ML基础油可针对习惯性流产有效。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">建议男性茉莉＋茶树泡澡消炎催情。茉莉&nbsp;2滴+玫瑰2滴香薰可催情。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">茉莉＋柠檬滴于内衣带四角处，帮助血液循环，丰胸。预防胸部下垂。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">月经不调：茉莉3滴+鼠尾草3+迷迭香3滴&nbsp;+天竺葵2滴。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">锁水保湿：茉莉1滴+薰衣草1+霍霍巴油&nbsp;5ml。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">7.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">安抚神经：茉莉3滴+甜橙3滴+檀香2滴。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十二、快乐鼠尾草精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1. 1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滴鼠尾草＋3－5滴薰衣草按摩腹部，治疗神经衰弱及失眠。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">收阴：1滴鼠尾草＋1－2滴佛手柑＋3－&nbsp;5滴薰衣草＋1滴茶树＋5ML&nbsp;基础油坐浴或泡浴收缩阴道，治妇科疾病。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十三、尤加利精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">春、夏、秋季最宜：5滴尤加利＋5滴广霍香可配合霍霍巴油涂于手脚可瘦身。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">防虫驱虫、净化空气：精油各5滴，尤加利＋薰衣草＋蜂蜜＋纯净水。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">治鼻炎，特别是慢性鼻炎：1滴尤加利＋1&nbsp;滴檀香，从额头一直涂于鼻尖。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十四、茴香精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">消除水肿：2滴茴香＋3－5滴丝柏泡脚可消除脚水肿。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十五、肉豆蔻精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">胃寒者可直接揉按。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">针对平时痛经：1滴肉豆蔻＋1滴姜油＋&nbsp;5ML基础油于腹部按 。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十六、迷迭香精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">排毒消炎、治腹泻。生发、去头屑。头发粗，易出油者（即脂溢性脱发）可调到洗发露中使用。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">消除皮肤水肿及眼袋肿胀，减肥。收紧皮 肤效果极佳。可用迷迭香＋玫瑰＋檀香＋茉莉。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">做眼部刮砂祛黑眼圈，眼袋：薰衣草＋迷迭香＋橙花。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">净化空气预防流感：2滴迷迭香＋2滴茶树 ＋100ML纯净水喷洒。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">治风湿骨痛：迷迭香＋柠檬。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">高血压慎用，低血压可用。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">7.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">消沮丧、平静、接触心灵。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十七、百里香精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1. 5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滴洋甘菊＋5滴百里香除霉味，可用棉球放置。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">百里香＋柠檬＋少量蜂蜜＋100ML纯净水喷洒，可除霉味。 长期开车者可喷于面部可提神。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十八、天竺葵精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">手脚冻疮：天竺葵＋洋甘菊＋薰衣草或柠檬各3－5滴＋手霜涂于患处，可有效治疗。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">脸上易长痘，淋巴不通的用其做淋巴排毒效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">平衡荷尔蒙及汗腺分泌、帮助溶解血块、利尿、排毒；平衡更年期及产后抑郁症。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滋补细胞、收敛毛孔、增加弹性、适合任何肤质。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">经前紧张：天竺葵2滴+薰衣草2滴+甜杏仁5ml按摩。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">消除焦虑：天竺葵3滴+檀香2滴+薰衣草3滴，香薰。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">7.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">油性皮肤可用天竺葵2滴+佛手柑1滴+葡萄籽5ml涂抹按摩。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">十九、葡萄柚（西柚） 精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">助消化、减头痛、推动淋巴、减重。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">去油性、痤疮、紧肤。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">开怀欢畅、减压、提高精力。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">勿在阳光下使用。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二十、玉桂精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">抗菌、对呼吸道有补预的效果。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">具有收敛、紧实作用，可用于皮肤松弛部分。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">对精疲力竭和虚弱，沮丧的安抚功效极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二十一、桉树精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">治发烧、头痛、感冒、肌肉酸痛、及呼吸系统疾病。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">补充皮肤氧气、适合色素沉者、皮肤较黄、暗疮皮肤、治愈蚊叮虫咬。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">增进活力，有振奋作用。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二十二、马丁香茅油（玫瑰草</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">)<br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" />1.&nbsp;调理气血，镇痛。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">保湿护肤、抗衰老、祛邹纹。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">减压、防止紧张、保持睡眠规律。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二十三、松针精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">治感冒、除汗臭、加速血液循环。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">洁净皮肤、活化细胞、畅通毛孔促进新陈代谢，适合任何皮肤。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">使头脑清晰，令人冷静、净化室内空气。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二十四、甜橙精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">治失眠，肚泻及喉部不适。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">有净化功能、改善皮肤缺水、收缩毛孔、 祛斑点。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">使人心情开朗，加强与人沟通。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">二十五、丝柏精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">丝柏＋檀香各2－3滴于热毛巾湿敷于咽喉处可治咽痛。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">丝柏＋广霍香可瘦身。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">好东西留着备用：二十六、佛手柑精油</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">佛手柑精油或薰衣草针对霉菌性阴道炎效果佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2. 1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">滴佛手柑＋2滴檀香对看起来油的外油内干的皮肤做面部刮痧，效果极佳。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">女性三宝精油：玫瑰、 茶树、 薰衣草</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">玫瑰：滴肚脐可预防妇科疾病；</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">茶树：世界公认的消炎杀菌佳品；</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;\" /><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">薰衣草：是一款百搭精油、跟任意一款精油搭配在一起可以增加任意一款精油的功效。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'楷体 serif\'; background-color: #ffc000; color: #c00000; font-size: 14pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">芳香疗法精油的养生</span></p>\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'楷体 serif\'; color: #4c4c4c; font-size: 14pt;\">芳香疗法它起源于</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">古埃及</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">等文明古国，早在</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">中国</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">公元前4500年就已发现植物具有治疗疾病的功效，在\"黄帝内经\"--记载着许多疾病发生的原因以及治疗的方法，其中对植物运用的智慧，是现代药草学家的指南。李时珍的《</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">本草纲目</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">》，则记载了两千多种药材（植物）、八千多种配方，是现代\"中医\"的根本。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">华佗</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">曾用香（</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">麝香</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">、丁香、檀香）制成粉末，装入丝绸制成的锦囊里，悬挂于室内，治疗呼吸道和上消化道疾病。而</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">埃及</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">人则发掘了芳香植物在肉体上和精神上的特质，记载</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">埃及艳后</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">克丽奥佩德拉以精油护肤，让全身充满香气使安东尼及</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">凯撒</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">大帝成为她的爱情俘虏。埃及艳后曾耗费巨资以&ldquo;香膏花园&rdquo;的植物来制作香油，让自己的手部柔软；另外，她喜欢在谈判时擦上茉莉香膏加上运用政治、外交手腕，让凯撒为她</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">平定</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">内乱。30年代 　正式提出\"芳香疗法\"一词的化学家</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">盖特</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">佛塞有一次在家族的</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">香水</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">公司研发新产品时，不慎发生</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">化学爆炸</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">伤及手部，情急之下，迅速把手伸进旁边的一瓶液体中，不可思议的是，灼伤的手竟然不那么痛了，水泡和伤口也减轻许多，而这碗液体正是</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">薰衣草精油</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">。盖特佛塞研究出薰衣草能消炎、杀菌疗伤的特性。医学专家发现人体常常处于疲劳状态，不自觉地发生心慌、呼吸困难等症状，严重时还可引起高血压、胃溃疡和变态反应性疾病等病症，而鲜花的芳香对这些病症具有良好的疗效。今天全世界各大美容养生会所，高档办公及家庭都在运用芳香疗法。芳香疗法可以透过人体的视觉、</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">触觉</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">和嗅觉来刺激大脑皮层，启迪人的思维，为人类提供精神上的慰藉，并解除心理和精神上的种种负荷及疾病，使人树立积极的人生态度。即为广义的&ldquo;芳香SPA&rdquo;，就是将植物芳香精油运用&ldquo;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">香熏</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">&rdquo;、&ldquo;按摩&rdquo;和&ldquo;沐浴&rdquo;等的方法，通过人体的嗅觉、</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">味觉</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">、触觉、视觉、</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">听觉</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">五大感觉功能，把植物的荷尔蒙，经由皮肤和呼吸系统吸收，进入脑下垂体，调整身体内分泌，从而对人在生理和心理上进行调整，使身心恢复协调，消除忧郁、焦虑、烦闷、愤怒等情绪和疲惫感，来达到一种身、心、灵皆俱舒畅的感觉，我们把它称其为&ldquo;五感疗法&rdquo;。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'楷体 serif\'; color: #4c4c4c; font-size: 14pt;\">芳香疗法的基本原理是运用植物精油的治疗力量来进行养生、美容、疗理身体和稳定情绪。它可以通过视觉、触觉和嗅觉来刺激大脑皮层，启发思维，解除心理和精神上的压力，令人身心舒畅。芳香疗法不仅能使人建立积极的人生态度，还增强人与人之间的沟通能力。点香薰精油的芳香疗法可以营造氛围{家庭点薰花朵精油增加浪漫，营业所点薰檀香招财}、增强免疫力{点薰薄荷防感冒}和提升工作效率{点薰柠檬茶树提神醒脑}。由于精油的分子比皮肤的分子要小得多，因此极易渗透入人体，精油经由毛孔进入，3分钟即可渗透到真皮层，5分钟进入至血液及淋巴，大约20分钟至6小时即可完全进入血液循环流至全身12小时完全排出体外。当按摩后精油在体内循环时，有一部分会被人体的器官、肌肉、</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">细胞</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">或神经纤维所吸收，从而达到精油治疗功能。现代人缺少运动用芳香精油按摩是促进肌肉运动达到健康的目的。同时按摩可以使运动拉伤的肌肉得到安抚，恢复健康的作用。所以芳香疗法也属于自然医疗的一种，是当今世界盛行的另类疗法。</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; font-family: \'楷体 serif\'; color: #4c4c4c; font-size: 14pt;\">精油</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\"> 芳香疗法分为：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">按摩法</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">适用症状：脸部护理、全身按摩、肌肉紧张、肩膀僵硬、减肥健胸、经痛、腹痛、便秘、抽筋等。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">建议用法：脸部：将精油<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">1-4</span>滴添加于<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">5ml</span>的基地油，搅匀后即可用来按摩。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">身体：将精油<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">5-8</span>滴添加于<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">10ml</span>的基底沐浴<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">/</span>按摩精油，搅匀后即可用来按摩。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">注意事项：每次所调配的精油宜尽快用完，以免变质。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">沐浴法</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">适用症状：全身机能调理、神经衰弱、解除疲劳、风湿关节痛、循环系统不佳、焦虑和沮丧、精神紧张等。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">建议用法：沐浴：将精油<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">5-8</span>滴添加于<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">10ml</span>的基底沐浴胶中，搅匀后即可用来淋浴。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">泡澡：将精油<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">5-8</span>滴加入装有温水的浴盆中，搅匀后即可用来泡澡。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">注意事项：使用精油沐浴以适中的水温为主，以免使精油挥发的太快。浸泡时需避免溅到眼睛。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">熏蒸法</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">适用症状：可安抚情绪、改善精神状况、失眠、增加记忆、净化空气、维护空气质量、提升情欲；并可消毒、避免呼吸道感染、及预防感冒等。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">建议用法：将熏香灯或熏香陶瓶加入八分满的水，再放入<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">5-6</span>滴的精油，点燃底部的无烟蜡烛可连续燃烧四个小时。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">注意事项：如果室内坪数较大，可酌量滴多一点精油或浓度高的精油。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">嗅吸法</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">适用症状：改善呼吸系统问题、鼻塞、气喘、醒脑、头晕、反胃等。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">建议用法：将<span style=\"max-width: 100%;\">2-3</span>滴的精油滴在手帕上，直接吸嗅即可。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285px; color: #3e3e3e; font-size: 14pt;\">注意事项：可选用较深色之手帕，避免精油使手帕变色&lsquo;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 7.5pt; line-height: 28.18181800842285px; min-height: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28.18181800842285